    "body": "<!--\r\n  Thank you for contributing to Neovim!\r\n  If this is your first time, check out https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#pull-requests-prs\r\n  for our PR guidelines.\r\n-->\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\nWith lsp servers like gopls that wont to return full semantic tokens for files that are too long. We fall back to viewport range based token retrievals which causes flickering when navigating.\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\n\r\nPull token ranges that overscan the visible window to prepare highlighting for future navs.\r\n\r\n## Open questions: \r\nShould this be a user configurable value? \r\n\r\nfixes: https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/40016",
